      <title>马拉松资产管理公司与韦伯斯特建立私人信贷合作关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/marathon-asset-management-webster-near-private-credit-tie-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份声明称，马拉松资产管理公司 (Marathon Asset Management) 和韦伯斯特金融公司 (Webster Financial Corp.) 正在组建一家私人信贷合资企业，专注于向私募股权支持的中型市场公司直接提供贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/marathon-asset-management-webster-near-private-credit-tie-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
